trans-unit.source: I receive the error "Another setup is already running. Please wait for it to finish before trying again."
trans-unit.target: I receive the error "Another setup is already running. Please wait for it to finish before trying again."

trans-unit.source: After attempting to install Visual Studio more than once, subsequent installation attempts result in the error "Another setup is already running.
trans-unit.target: After attempting to install Visual Studio more than once, subsequent installation attempts result in the error "Another setup is already running.

trans-unit.source: Please wait for it to finish before trying again".
trans-unit.target: Please wait for it to finish before trying again".

trans-unit.source: Only one instance of a Visual Studio installation can run at a time.
trans-unit.target: Only one instance of a Visual Studio installation can run at a time.

trans-unit.source: Make sure that there is only one instance open.
trans-unit.target: Make sure that there is only one instance open.

trans-unit.source: If you receive this error even when there is only one instance of Visual Studio open, try restarting your machine to end the processes that can cause this issue.
trans-unit.target: If you receive this error even when there is only one instance of Visual Studio open, try restarting your machine to end the processes that can cause this issue.

trans-unit.source:
If restarting your machine does not resolve the problem, try the following:
  1. Open Task Manager.
trans-unit.target:
If restarting your machine does not resolve the problem, try the following:
  1. Open Task Manager.

trans-unit.source: • If there are more than one, select them and choose End Task.
trans-unit.target: • If there are more than one, select them and choose End Task.
